  Bump, keyword ~amd64.

  13 Feb 2008; Christian Faulhammer <opfer@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  add no-herd

  31 Jan 2008; Donnie Berkholz <dberkholz@gentoo.org>;
  -files/virtinst-0.103.0-accelerate.patch,
  -files/virtinst-0.103.0-default-net.patch,
